data.description:
Large two story home positioned on a large lot in a quiet neighborhood. 4 bedroom/ 3 bathroom newly remodeled with all the modern furnishings with all original hardwood floors throughout. All new kitchen and paint new roof in 2021. The outdoor living space is equally amazing featuring large covered pergola overlooking the new inground pool to spend your summers with several mature large trees for that summer shade! Short drive to I-35 or Oklahoma city for those commuters! Don't wait to schedule your showing this home is perfect balance of modern and traditional and will be someone's forever home! SELLER OFFERING $2000 IN BUYERS INCENTIVES!
Agent related to seller.
